<p>I agree with this. For one we have the toaster already, for two it's … well … I can admire the quirk and the unique way of writing up an SCP doc but … this should be 575-J. Gonna have to downvote.</p>
<p>The toaster also seemed like it should have been a J but it wasn't funny at all. It was horrifying once you got past the friendly sounding language and realized what it could do to you.</p>
